en: Dorothy Gracy, daughter of one of the college professors, spills Sopjes in jiu-jitsu demonstration

Dorothy Gracy, daughter of a Middle Tennessee State College professor, flips Sopjes in a jiu-jitsu demonstration. During a homefront war bond rally on the Murfreesboro public square, the College Training Detachment hosted demonstrations and speeches for the entertainment of the assembled crowd.
